              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h1 class="center">Is your website slow?</h1>
          <h2 class="h3 center"> Do I need to pinch & zoom a PDF to see your pricelist? </h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mean_title mean_title--second">
        <div class="wrap flex flex_cols flex_align_center flex_justify_center">
          <div class="mean_icon">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0.5 400.5 400 400"
              class="brand_color outlined icon--jumping"
            >
              <path
                fill="none"
                d="M356.654 441.236c7.189-6.6 7.685-17.773 1.105-24.983-6.564-7.216-17.731-7.701-24.961-1.129l-106.497 97.28-170.371-.411c-9.767.203-17.518 8.288-17.313 18.054.199 9.479 7.835 17.114 17.313 17.313h103.846v63.846l-72.438.069a21.25 21.25 0 0 0-17.462 9.21 21.21 21.21 0 0 0-2.326 19.616l32.428 84.505a21.236 21.236 0 0 0 19.815 13.632c2.532 0 5.102-.464 7.599-1.429 10.934-4.182 16.406-16.436 12.223-27.37a.182.182 0 0 0-.011-.028l-21.378-55.692 95.098-.094.121 58.271-83.782 38.161c-10.61 4.985-15.169 17.628-10.184 28.238 4.901 10.43 17.229 15.045 27.775 10.396l96.246-43.842a21.174 21.174 0 0 0 12.402-19.36l-.331-191.948 101.083-92.305z"
              ></path>
              <path
                fill="none"
                d="M219.338 472.87c0 19.317-15.66 34.995-34.963 34.995-19.329 0-35.002-15.678-35.002-34.995.002-19.329 15.673-34.999 35.002-34.999 19.299 0 34.963 15.68 34.963 34.999z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h1 class="center">We can fix that.</h1>
          <h2 class="h3 center"> We offer all-inclusive packages for any budget! </h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="product_grid top_pad--big">
      <div id="landing-page" class="looper__link card bestvalue" title="LANDING PAGE package">
        <div class="product_text">
          <h2 class="center">Compact Website</h2>

          <h3 class="h4 center color_black">All-included package</h3>

          <h4 class="h3 center">
