        <div class="product_text">
          <h2 class="center">Awesome Design</h2>

          <h3 class="h4 center color_black">All-included package</h3>

          <h4 class="h3 center">
            Customised design for your needs. Name, Hosting and SSL included for one whole year. <small>
              50 Euro/year after that.
            </small>
          </h4>

          <p class="center">
